Target features for v1.0
========================
- Builds from stage3.
    * Qemu (done)
    * Register binfmt_misc
    * chroot + emerge
- Working upgrade mechanism.
    * kernel upgrade/switch (u-boot can be helpful)
    * rootfs upgrade/switch
        = use an initramfs to overwrite rootfs during a reboot cycle
        = dual-rootfs, upgrade B image, and switch on reboot
        = other upgrade mechanisms TBD
- CI builds
- licensing
- versioning

